INSTALL
-------

Install git, nodejs, node-express, npm and mongodb

Clone repository:

git clone https://github.com/vesapehkonen/jatrailmap.git

Install node modules:

  cd jatrailmap/nodejs
  npm install

Default request body size is 102400 bytes, change it to bigger by adding line 

  limit = 1024 * 1024 * 100;

to the file node_modules/raw-body/index.js, after the line 99.

RUN
---

Start server
npm start

Start browser with an address http://localhost:3000
